io.neba.core.rendering

Class BeanRendererFactoryConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.neba.core.rendering.BeanRendererFactoryConfiguration

  • @Service(value=BeanRendererFactoryConfiguration.class)
@Properties(value=@Property(name="service.vendor",value="neba.io"))
public class BeanRendererFactoryConfiguration
extends Object
    The sole purpose of this class is to provide service component runtime (SCR) metadata enabling service configuration via the OSGi console. The metadata is generated from the SCR annotations of this class by the maven-scr-plugin during build time.
    The generated metadata is used in the blueprint configuration of this module to configure the BeanRendererFactoryImpl.
    Author:
    Olaf Otto
